author: Danielle Berjikian
description:
“Why should English people pay for [a foreign national] to have a house?” That is something one third-world migrant was not able to answer, but that did not stop him from demanding the people of the U.K. “give [him] anything [he] needs.”

Americans get a rash of shit for our politics but at least we switch it up if people don’t like what’s going on.

It’s hilarious how countries like England have voted for this for 50 years straight and don’t forsee any potential consequences. https://t.co/hUXXReMAWY
— Nick Watts (@NICKWATTS__) May 15, 2025
title: Migrant lectures reporter why legal citizens owe him a brand new house

author: Danielle Berjikian
description:
Even if the most radical leftist must adhere to the notion that no human is illegal, why must they affirm this delusion to the point that the worst scum on this planet are treated as “human beings?” Because, as far as I am concerned, murderers and child predators are most definitely not worthy of human rights, but that is apparently not the case for one blue-haired woman.

Savanah Hernandez interviewed protesters outside of a Newark ICE detention center, and the answers were worse than you think.


“You think child rapists deserve dignity?”

“Absolutely, I do”

I went and talked to protesters outside of the ICE detention center in Newark, because I wanted to know why they were defending the criminal illegal aliens inside:
title: Blue-haired leftist makes her unhinged case on why child predators deserve "dignity" outside an ICE detention center
